I still have some left. I will give all of them to you.

5
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,610
This purse is quite exquisite.

6
00:01:54,730 --> 00:01:57,960
I seem to have one that looks similar.

7
00:02:01,550 --> 00:02:03,810
May I be bold enough to ask,

8
00:02:03,810 --> 00:02:05,860
where did Talented Lady Wu

9
00:02:05,860 --> 00:02:08,920
get your sachet?

10
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:13,320
My own sister at home went to the Western Market and bought it from a Hu merchant that she was familiar with.

11
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:16,110
If Attire Expert Zhuo wants, I can ask her

12
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:19,660
to buy more next time she sees them again.

13
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:23,830
This servant is only admiring the embroidery technique on the sachet.

14
00:02:23,830 --> 00:02:25,790
That's why I was bold enough to ask about it.

15
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:28,640
I would not dare to bother Talented Lady Wu.

16
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:30,710
It's no bother.

17
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:43,300
[Bureau of Imperial Attire]

18
00:03:01,550 --> 00:03:03,510
Physician Dou,

19
00:03:06,460 --> 00:03:08,920
show me your sachet.

20
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:16,850
Did you make it yourself?

21
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:18,890
Of course not.

22
00:03:22,430 --> 00:03:26,830
Then those purses that Xiao Shunzi bought, you made them?

23
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:31,660
All the purses were bought by Xiao Shunzi from the Hu merchant.

24
00:03:31,660 --> 00:03:33,960
Let's just forget it, if you don't want to tell the truth.

25
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:38,380
You are trying so hard to lie, there must be a reason.

26
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:42,910
I don't intend to keep questioning, but I'd like to remind you of something.

27
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:46,880
If you have decided to lie, then don't show any loopholes.

28
00:03:46,880 --> 00:03:50,130
Even though your sachet is made with exquisite craftsmanship,

29
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:54,620
but it is old. It looks about ten years, or at least eight years old.

30
00:03:54,620 --> 00:03:58,020
Also, the fabric used is not any ordinary fabric used by civilians.

31
00:03:58,020 --> 00:04:00,590
Those that are sold by Xiao Douzi

32
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:03,870
are newly made with high-quality fabrics used in the palace.

33
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,870
Attire Expert Zhuo was momentarily inattentive

34
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:08,770
and got fooled by your little trick.

35
00:04:08,770 --> 00:04:13,520
Once she carefully thinks it over later, she will definitely realize some inkling.

36
00:04:17,620 --> 00:04:21,530
Luckily there is still a chance to remedy the situation.

37
00:04:21,530 --> 00:04:25,740
You can use the ordinary civilian fabric, mixed with some old fabric,

38
00:04:25,740 --> 00:04:28,740
make another batch of purses and distribute them.

39
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:30,940
Remember to send one over to me.

40
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:33,920
If my guess is right, in a few days,

41
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:37,910
Attire Expert Zhuo will find an excuse to come to my place about the sachet.

42
00:04:37,910 --> 00:04:40,280
At that time, if I don't have any,

43
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:43,210
I won't be able to keep helping you.

44
00:04:50,510 --> 00:04:54,080
Talented Lady Wu is truly astounding.

45
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,580
Excellent writing!

46
00:06:10,910 --> 00:06:13,570
[Mist Locking Mountaintop Locking Mist]

47
00:06:13,570 --> 00:06:15,300
[Pei Xingjian]

48
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:17,020
Attendant.

49
00:06:18,450 --> 00:06:20,990
Young Master Pei, what would you like?

50
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:23,400
Change that banner.

51
00:06:23,400 --> 00:06:26,500
This... Young Master Pei, you probably don't know.

52
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:29,110
The phrase on top was left by a noble young master.

53
00:06:29,110 --> 00:06:30,950
He said he wanted to challenge the elites in Chang'an.

54
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:34,220
Whoever can match with a bottom phrase, he will provide ten days of payment for wine.

55
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:36,480
If no one can do it, then...

56
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,700
Then it means the scholars in Chang'an are useless.

57
00:06:39,700 --> 00:06:43,520
He even said he will ruin our Drunken Fragrance Tower's reputation.

58
00:06:47,500 --> 00:06:50,950
"Mist locking" mountaintop locking mist.

59
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:53,490
It is indeed ingenious.

60
00:06:53,490 --> 00:06:58,000
There was a big fog yesterday morning. Drunken Fragrance Tower was covered by the thick fog which didn't disperse for a long time.

61
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:00,350
The top phrase was inspired by the scene.

62
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:04,180
That young master also said the bottom phrase must also be inspired by this scene so as to become a couplet.

63
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:07,830
Now that the two-day limit is about to be reached.

64
00:07:07,830 --> 00:07:11,250
I really don't dare to arbitrarily move it. Please be understanding, Young Master Pei.

65
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,240
Find another place to write then.

66
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,940
No.

67
00:07:17,220 --> 00:07:19,830
I just want this place.

68
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:27,450
Good skill.

69
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:32,160
Let's go take a look.

70
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:34,580
- Go.
- Let's go.

71
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:12,190
This is written well.

72
00:08:12,190 --> 00:08:15,990
Also in line with the phrase.

73
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:46,640
You've come. We have found for you the 30-year vintage wine kept in the cellar.

74
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:51,380
Good. The two-day limit has arrived. Has anyone come up with the bottom phrase?
[Crown Prince Li Zhi]

75
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:54,690
Our Drunken Fragrance Tower is the gathering place of all the gifted scholars and famous writers.

76
00:08:54,690 --> 00:08:59,380
It's just that the two-day limit given by Young Master was really too short.

77
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,110
Why not extend it a few more days?

78
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:04,030
Someone will definitely be able to match with a bottom phrase by then.

79
00:09:04,030 --> 00:09:07,130
This is really meaningful.

80
00:09:07,130 --> 00:09:09,130
- Waiter!
- I'm here.

81
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:11,160
Who ate a bear heart and leopard gall?  (Who was so audacious?)

82
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:13,670
How dare he erase Hisâ€”

83
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:16,590
...my young master's top phrase?

84
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:20,630
Young Master, don't be upset. Your top phrase is still there.

85
00:09:20,630 --> 00:09:23,750
If you don't believe it, just look. It's an acrostic poem.

86
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:25,920
Laughingly I ask how much an exam candidate is worth.

87
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:28,460
Ten years of study fills me with ambition.

88
00:09:28,460 --> 00:09:30,820
These two lines are really fierce.

89
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:35,870
The entire piece criticizes current affairs. The words are really sharp as swords and blades.

90
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,470
Which crazy rascal wrote this?

91
00:09:38,470 --> 00:09:40,690
How dare he criticize Great Tang's imperial exam?

92
00:09:40,690 --> 00:09:43,790
This... I am not good at reading and writing.

93
00:09:43,790 --> 00:09:45,830
The signature is written at the end of the poem.

94
00:09:45,830 --> 00:09:48,780
Will the noble guest please take a look himself?

95
00:09:50,010 --> 00:09:51,670
Shouyue?
[Shouyue written at Drunken Fragrance Tower]

96
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:54,260
Who is this Shouyue?

97
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:57,320
This Shouyue is a student at the Imperial Academy's Simen College.

98
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,990
His surname is Pei, given name is Xingjian, courtesy name is Shouyue.

99
00:09:59,990 --> 00:10:03,030
Shouyue is quick-witted with a fierce literary style.

100
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:05,220
His calligraphy and martial arts

101
00:10:05,220 --> 00:10:07,810
are famous in Chang'an.

102
00:10:07,810 --> 00:10:09,080
It's a minuscule skill.

103
00:10:09,080 --> 00:10:13,040
If he is really skilled, he should have matched my young master's top phrase.

104
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:15,970
- Ingenious!
- Ingenious?

105
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:19,980
Young Master, how is it ingenious?

106
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:23,420
That Pei Xingjian has matched my phrase.

107
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:25,100
A'Sheng, look over there.

108
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:26,710
The first words across from the top phrase.

109
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:29,790
The bottom phrase is the third word from the bottom.

110
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:33,150
My top phrase is "Mist Locking Mountaintop Locking Mist."
[Read from right to left]

111
00:10:33,150 --> 00:10:37,220
His bottom phrase is "Wine Entered Sadness Entered Wine."

112
00:10:37,220 --> 00:10:39,290
It's nothing rare to write an acrostic poem,

113
00:10:39,290 --> 00:10:41,930
but to hide both the top and the bottom phrases,

114
00:10:41,930 --> 00:10:44,380
this is the first time I've seen so.

115
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:46,220
Such is Pei Xingjian!

116
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:49,510
To so cleverly think of such a matching method,

117
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:52,220
this Drunken Fragrance Tower is indeed full of hidden dragons and crouching tigers. (Full of hidden talents)

118
00:10:53,380 --> 00:10:56,210
A'Sheng, pay the cashier.

119
00:10:56,210 --> 00:10:59,550
- I want to invite him to drink this 30-year vintage wine.
- Yes.

120
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:01,340
- Attendant.
- I'm here.

121
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:03,090
Give my message to Young Master Pei.

122
00:11:03,090 --> 00:11:05,490
I'll meet him five days later at Drunken Fragrance Tower.

123
00:11:05,490 --> 00:11:08,030
Yes, I've got it.

124
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:13,030
The brush strokes are strong, too.

125
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,260
Talented Lady, Physician Dou has arrived.

126
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:35,450
Physician Dou greets Talented Lady Wu.

127
00:11:35,450 --> 00:11:37,970
You are here to deliver the sachet, right?

128
00:11:37,970 --> 00:11:39,970
Let me take a look.

129
00:11:49,020 --> 00:11:51,810
This sachet is very similar to the ones sold by Xiao Shunzi.

130
00:11:51,810 --> 00:11:55,520
Except the material used is different.

131
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,160
I wasn't wrong, right?

132
00:11:57,160 --> 00:12:00,050
All these sachets were made by you.

133
00:12:00,050 --> 00:12:02,500
Talented Lady Wu, I am ashamed.

134
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:05,590
I had my own reason and difficulties for not telling.

135
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:07,310
In this palace,

136
00:12:07,310 --> 00:12:11,480
who doesn't have secrets and difficulties?

137
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,690
I will not force you.

138
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:18,450
Talented Lady, the guards at the door

139
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:21,860
said Attire Expert Zhou is here.

140
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:29,100
As expected, she came at such a coincidence.

141
00:12:29,970 --> 00:12:33,210
That day, I said I had the same sachet.

142
00:12:33,210 --> 00:12:35,380
Maybe Attire Expert Zhou

143
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:38,960
has come to ask about the sachet.

144
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:42,030
But don't you worry, Attire Expert Zhou

145
00:12:42,030 --> 00:12:44,880
will not have any suspicion towards you.

146
00:12:45,570 --> 00:12:49,780
Send Physician Dou out through the back door.

147
00:12:50,350 --> 00:12:53,600
I thank Talented Lady Wu for saving me and Xiao Shunzi.

148
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:55,300
I owe you an explanation.

149
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:58,770
One day, I will reveal my reasoning to Talented Lady.

150
00:12:58,770 --> 00:13:01,510
I help you because I can see that you are kind-hearted.

151
00:13:01,510 --> 00:13:06,110
Let's count this as me returning you the favor for Talented Lady Di.

152
00:13:08,910 --> 00:13:12,010
Master, there is such a sachet at Talented Lady Wu's.

153
00:13:12,010 --> 00:13:14,650
This means that Xiao Shunzi and Physician Dou didn't lie.

154
00:13:14,650 --> 00:13:17,370
Indeed the sachet came from the Western Market.

155
00:13:17,370 --> 00:13:19,940
The Bureau of Imperial Attire got many rewards from my lady.

156
00:13:19,940 --> 00:13:22,720
I'm just asking you to make her one last new attire.

157
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,670
But all of you are making a ruckus.

158
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:27,040
We make clothes for a living.

159
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:31,120
We don't have such a time to make clothes for the dead.

160
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:34,270
I'm actually not impressed by the workmanship and morals at the Bureau of Imperial Attire.

161
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:37,250
I heard Physician Dou's

162
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:40,320
skills and morals are better than any of you.

163
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,580
I will go and beg him.

164
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:52,830
Just now what you said about Physician Dou is true?

165
00:13:52,830 --> 00:13:56,400
I can't be wrong. Talented Lady Di's personal maid told me.

166
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:59,570
Talent Lady Di died of an illness, so Talented Lady Wu brought a new gown to see her off.

167
00:13:59,570 --> 00:14:03,420
Unexpectedly, Talent Lady Di was already wearing a beautiful gown.

168
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:05,420
Talented Lady Wu asked and found out

169
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:07,790
that Talented Lady Di's gown was actually

170
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:10,480
made by Physician Dou of the Courtyard of Misfortune.

171
00:14:23,690 --> 00:14:26,040
Master, based on what she said,

172
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:29,790
Talented Lady Wu and Physician Dou already knew each other.

173
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:31,570
Do you now suspect that

174
00:14:31,570 --> 00:14:35,890
Talent Lady Wu helped Physician Dou and Xiao Shunzi to lie?

175
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:37,550
That's right.

176
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:41,510
That original sachet was also found at Physician Dou's place.

177
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,180
Furthermore,

178
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:47,230
he is actually a hidden expert at dressmaking.

179
00:14:47,880 --> 00:14:50,580
No, this can't be a coincidence.

180
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:53,770
How can there be such a coincidence in the world?

181
00:14:58,730 --> 00:15:01,940
I have to thoroughly clear this up.

182
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:06,020
[Courtyard of Misfortune]

183
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:10,530
I've found it!

184
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,680
I've finally found it.

185
00:15:14,820 --> 00:15:18,870
Physician Dou entered the palace at the age of 12 during the 12th year of the Zhenguan Era.

186
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:22,770
Does that file say who his parents were? How did he enter the palace?

187
00:15:24,070 --> 00:15:28,230
Physician Dou has no father and no mother. When Sun Dechang left the palace to run errands,

188
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:30,460
he found this orphan alongside the street.

189
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:32,700
Originally, he was supposed to be castrated to become a little eunuch.

190
00:15:32,700 --> 00:15:35,600
But the Courtyard of Misfortune was missing a physician in charge of sanitation,

191
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:38,680
so Sun Decheng let him learn some medical skills

192
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:41,050
and filled that open position at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

193
00:15:41,050 --> 00:15:44,290
No father and no mother?

194
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:52,270
[Bureau of Imperial Attire]

195
00:16:05,170 --> 00:16:06,490
Qiniang,

196
00:16:06,490 --> 00:16:10,780
for the new people that we want to work here this year, has the Directorate of Eunuchs allocated anyone yet?

197
00:16:10,780 --> 00:16:14,570
Not yet. I think It should be in a couple of days.

198
00:16:18,220 --> 00:16:22,210
Eunuch Liu, even though the Courtyard of Misfortune isn't a place of high status,

199
00:16:22,210 --> 00:16:25,220
you still can't randomly stick someone in here.

200
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:28,720
[Wei Lin]

201
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:33,330
Unclean hands, insincere heart, I won't take him.
(Unclean hands means someone who steals)

202
00:16:35,750 --> 00:16:37,410
Eunuch Sun,

203
00:16:37,410 --> 00:16:41,100
Wei Lin was originally a smart and able person.

204
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:42,860
This time, he made some mistakes.

205
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:46,120
Otherwise, he would have climbed up higher.

206
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:49,320
There are many places that are short of people. We aren't short here at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

207
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,900
Why do you have to push him to my place?

208
00:16:53,450 --> 00:16:55,720
Since the Courtyard of Misfortune isn't short of helpers,

209
00:16:55,720 --> 00:17:00,220
could Eunuch Sun let me have Physician Dou then?

210
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:04,460
Attire Expert Zhuo must be joking.

211
00:17:04,460 --> 00:17:06,320
Physician Dou is my foster son.

212
00:17:06,320 --> 00:17:09,300
He specializes in sanitation at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

213
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,760
He is indispensable at the Courtyard of Misfortune.

214
00:17:13,070 --> 00:17:17,060
They say that Physician Dou is quite talented at dressmaking and embroidery.

215
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:21,780
Even Talented Lady Wu was impressed by his skills.

216
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:24,030
I would like to make an exception for him,

217
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:26,780
transfer him to the Bureau of Imperial Attire and teach him well.

218
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:29,000
It should be better than working as a sanitation physician

219
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,470
at the Courtyard of Misfortune, right?

220
00:17:34,150 --> 00:17:36,330
I will teach my own people.

221
00:17:36,330 --> 00:17:39,170
Attire Expert Zhuo doesn't need to bother.

222
00:17:41,990 --> 00:17:44,830
Why don't you follow him quickly?

223
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:48,650
[Archive of Official Correspondence]

224
00:17:48,650 --> 00:17:50,630
Attire Expert Zhuo.

225
00:17:51,310 --> 00:17:53,530
Eunuch Liu.

226
00:18:09,420 --> 00:18:11,140
Xiao Douzi.

227
00:18:11,870 --> 00:18:13,600
Xiao Douzi.

228
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:17,310
Foster Father.

229
00:18:24,050 --> 00:18:26,950
Foster Father, it's still ten days before my birthday.

230
00:18:26,950 --> 00:18:29,430
Are you remembering wrong?

231
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,550
Before you eat the long-life noodles,

232
00:18:33,310 --> 00:18:36,080
kowtow a few times to your mother first.

233
00:18:54,880 --> 00:18:58,470
[Memorial Tablet for Attire Expert An]

234
00:18:58,470 --> 00:19:01,350
Attire Expert An, in another ten days,

235
00:19:01,350 --> 00:19:03,720
it will be Liuli's 18th birthday.

236
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:07,620
I originally wanted to comply with your last wish

237
00:19:07,620 --> 00:19:11,480
to let her leave the palace when she reaches 18 years of age.

238
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:15,990
But I can't. Liuli takes after you too much.

239
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:19,080
She casually makes a dress, embroiders a flower.

240
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:21,540
It will attract others' attention.

241
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:23,960
It's really not possible to hide.

242
00:19:23,960 --> 00:19:28,260
We can't wait anymore.

243
00:19:28,260 --> 00:19:30,170
That's why this morning,

244
00:19:30,170 --> 00:19:33,950
I went to the Imperial Academy of Medicine to complain about her.

